        "Description": "Leader or someone near leadership of that small terrorist organisation has been captured by militia and is hold hostage in their camp. From what we&apos;ve heard they want to absorb our target organisation into theirs, forming even stronger army.\r\rWhile we don&apos;t really care about the militia itself, conjoining these two will make identify members of our target organisation almost impossible.\r\rEliminate the hostage and all people who could know about him, including guard watching cameras.",
